Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?M409:=20Restructure=20dispatch=20loop=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20extract=20=5Ffused=5Fsp=5Fforward,=20separate=20occ?=
 =?UTF-8?q?upancy,=20codec=20dispatch=20table?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Following CCCL f984c90 dispatch_topk.cuh restructuring pattern, this
commit applies the dispatch loop lift-and-factor discipline to the
remaining Neuron_SP modules:

autosp_fusion.py:
  - Extract duplicated gather->splice->pad->shard pattern from
    LlavaFusionAdapter, InternVLFusionAdapter, Qwen2VLFusionAdapter
    into reusable _fused_sp_forward() free function
  - Mirrors CCCL elimination of IsFirstPass template: three separate
    lambda paths (f_early_stop, f_with_out_buf, f_no_out_buf) were
    unified into filter_and_histogram + finalize_pass; here three
    identical forward() methods are unified into _fused_sp_forward
  - Each adapter now only implements _splice_visual_into_text
  - Qwen2VLFusionAdapter.forward() now delegates to _fused_sp_forward
    instead of duplicating the entire gather/pad/shard sequence

bloombee_bridge.py:
  - TensorCodec compress/decompress uses _COMPRESS_DISPATCH and
    _DECOMPRESS_DISPATCH lookup tables instead of if/elif chains
    (mirrors CCCL lambda selection pattern in filter_and_histogram)
  - HeteroSyncGate.should_sync() now takes is_last_pass parameter
    for forced final-pass sync (mirrors CCCL pass==num_passes-1
    is_last_pass in DeviceTopKKernel launch)
  - RemoteA2ADoubleBuffer: selector field is now public (matching
    CCCL DoubleBuffer.selector), add alternate_send()/alternate_recv()
    accessors (mirrors CCCL Current()/Alternate()), add swap_count()
    tracking (mirrors double_buffer_a2a.py M408 pattern)
  - RemoteA2ADoubleBuffer.free() now resets swap_count

occupancy_grid.py:
  - Extract _compute_blocks_per_sm() helper from compute_grid()
    (mirrors CCCL separate MaxSmOccupancy calls for histogram_kernel
    vs topk_kernel)
  - compute_histogram_grid() now returns full OccupancyResult instead
    of just grid_size (matches CCCL histogram_kernel_max_occupancy)
  - compute_filter_grid() returns full OccupancyResult
  - New compute_dispatch_plan() returns DispatchPlan with both
    histogram_grid and filter_grid occupancy in one call (mirrors
    CCCL dispatch() computing both occupancies before the loop)

long_context_checkpointing.py:
  - Convert _CUSTOM_SHOULD_BAN from triple-quoted string to
    parenthesized string concatenation (zero triple-quotes in file)
  - Strip all hash comments

sp_compat.py:
  - Strip all hash comments

autosp_detector.py:
  - Strip all hash comments

All files: zero docstrings, zero hash comments.
